Fourth Department,

January, 1957

(January 9, 1957) George Colon Contracting Corporation, Appellant, v. Joseph J. Morrison et al., Constituting the Watertown Housing Authority, Respondents.

— Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Present — McCurn, P. J., Vaughan, Kimball and Williams, JJ. [See 2 A D 2d 869.]
